data.description: Welcome to the epitome of home sweet home! Step into luxury with a screened patio that's practically begging for your morning coffee sessions. Wait, there's more–an additional deck, because why settle for one when you can have two? Wandering onto the back deck you'll find beautiful mature trees & a fenced yard. If the sun is feeling a bit generous, fear not–solar panels grace the roof, making this home as eco-friendly as it is charming.   Inside, you'll be floored (literally) by the engineered hardwood floors. All 3 bedrooms & living room feature a tray or vaulted ceiling ensuring that even your dreams have room to breathe. Primary suite: two separate vanities-sharing is overrated, jetted soaker tub, & a spacious walk-in closet. Wide open spaces makes this home functional dream come true!
